Vanilla Ice Goes Amish - Season 2, Episode 6




Amish Field of Dreams

Rob's getting ready to head back to Florida but wants to do something to thank his Amish hosts. When Kevin tells him about a popular community center baseball field that has no place for folks to hang out, Rob and the team go to work on bleachers and a concession stand built on an old Amish horse wagon.




Original Air Date: 15-Nov-2014
